---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="lg:col-span-1" rowSpan="lg:row-span-5" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-sm font-light">
    <p>
      I’m a full stack developer who works across frontend and backend, usually
      building web apps, APIs, and database-driven systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      My core stack includes JavaScript/TypeScript, Node.js + Express, Laravel,
      MySQL, React, and Astro. I focus on solutions that stay simple, fast, and
      reliable.
    </p>

    <div class="hidden sm:block">
      <p class="m-0 text-gray-400 font-medium">Education</p>
      <p class="m-0">BS in Information Technology · 2020–2024</p>
      <p class="m-0">Asian College of Technology</p>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden sm:block">
      <p class="m-0 text-gray-400 font-medium">Experience</p>
      <p class="m-0"><b>Full Stack Developer</b> · Cubic Solutions Inc (2025–2026)</p>
      <p class="m-0"><b>Backend Developer</b> · Proweaver Inc (Jun–Oct 2024)</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Card>
